# intinal homeless ship target
get_fleet_homeless_ship_target = {
	
	#cal_homeless_ship_resource_country = yes
	every_owned_ship = {
		limit = { is_any_type_homeless_ship = yes }
		cal_homeless_ship_resource = yes
		prev = { change_variable = { which = tracking_caculation_homeless_ship value = 1 } }
	}
	every_owned_ship = {
		limit = { 
			is_any_type_homeless_ship = yes 
			NOT = { has_ship_flag = tracking_caculation_homeless_ship } 
		}
		save_calculation_homeless_ship_target = yes
	}

}
